conversation_memory_summary_prompt_templ:
Participants
- {participant_a_name}
- {participant_b_name}

Existing Summary
{existing_summary}

Recent Lines
{recent_lines}

Task
Write one short session-memory summary for future prompt grounding.
- Keep it under 240 characters.
- Focus on what shifted between them: trust, openness, resistance, what pattern Noa revealed or avoided.
- Do not invent anything.
- Write in plain third-person prose, not bullets.

