{subtext}

Recent Memory
{recent_memory}

Latest Line From Target
{other_person_message}

Spoken Line
- {spoken_line}

Task
Return exactly one label describing the speaker's intent: NONE, WARM, FLIRTY, VALIDATING, or CHALLENGING.
- WARM: gentle affection
- FLIRTY: romantic or playful teasing
- VALIDATING: telling the target their feelings make sense and are okay
- CHALLENGING: pushing the target to confront an issue or look deeper

